userID (GUID) -- use GUID instead of INT for uniqueness and security\nusername (email) -- preferably email\npasswordHash (with salt merged)\nnonceUsePassword (or passwordResetToken) -- for password reset\nalternativeContactEmail\nuserStatusID (FK to a lookup table with statuses like: active, disabled, etc.)\ndateCreated\ndateUpdated\nlastPasswordUpdate\nlastLogon\nfailedLoginAttempts (to track failed login attempts)\naccountLockoutTime (to lock out the account after multiple failed attempts)